    "description": "Axis Bank Asia Pacific Associates invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Risk Analyst at our Kochi location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Axis Bank Asia Pacific Associates:\nAxis Bank Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Referral bonus program\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Axis Bank Asia Pacific Associates!",
